## Tooling (Node / TypeScript)

- `npm install` тАФ install deps ┬╖ `npm install <pkg>` тАФ add a dep
- `npm test` тАФ tests (vitest) ┬╖ `npm run check` тАФ biome lint + format ┬╖ `npm run typecheck` тАФ tsc
- CI gates **changed-file coverage**: every changed source line must be covered, via `@vitest/coverage-v8` + `scripts/check-coverage.mjs`.
- Layout: `src/`, tests in `tests/`. Node >= {{ node_version }}, ESM (`"type": "module"`).
